&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;262&quot; data-end=&quot;279&quot;&gt;About Aktos&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;280&quot; data-end=&quot;716&quot;&gt;Debt collection software is broken — and we&#39;re fixing it. Aktos is a modern platform purpose-built for debt collection agencies to run their entire business, replacing the patchwork of legacy systems they’ve had to rely on for decades. Our software is fast, intuitive, and automates the repetitive and error-prone workflows that cost teams time and money. We&#39;re building the next-generation infrastructure for the industry — and beyond.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;718&quot; data-end=&quot;999&quot;&gt;We&#39;re a tight-knit team of builders, dreamers, and doers backed by world-class investors like &lt;strong data-start=&quot;812&quot; data-end=&quot;819&quot;&gt;8VC&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong data-start=&quot;824&quot; data-end=&quot;840&quot;&gt;Crew Capital&lt;/strong&gt;. Our customers love us, and our growth is accelerating. Now we’re looking for our &lt;strong data-start=&quot;923&quot; data-end=&quot;953&quot;&gt;Founding Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt; to bring Aktos to the next wave of customers.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr data-start=&quot;1001&quot; data-end=&quot;1004&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;1006&quot; data-end=&quot;1026&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1027&quot; data-end=&quot;1338&quot;&gt;As our first full-time sales hire, you’ll play a pivotal role in shaping our go-to-market strategy, directly closing deals, and setting the foundation for a world-class sales motion. This is a rare opportunity to get in early at a fast-moving startup and help define how we sell, who we sell to, and how we win.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1340&quot; data-end=&quot;1514&quot;&gt;You’ll work closely with our CEO, product, and customer success teams to deeply understand the customer journey and help agencies adopt software that actually works for them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1340&quot; data-end=&quot;1514&quot;&gt;The sales stack we use:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1340&quot; data-end=&quot;1514&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;CRM&lt;/strong&gt;: HubSpot&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1340&quot; data-end=&quot;1514&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Prospecting Tools&lt;/strong&gt;: ZoomInfo, Apollo&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1340&quot; data-end=&quot;1514&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Other&lt;/strong&gt;: Grain, Slack, Zoom, etc.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
