&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Aktos was founded by seasoned Product and Engineering leaders who have worked at companies such as Zenefits, TikTok, Meta, LinkedIn, Google, Apple, Amazon, WeWork, Flatiron Health (acquired by Booking.com). We are experts at building, launching, and scaling word-class software platforms— rest assured, if you join us you will be working with and learning from the best.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Stack:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Frontend - ReactJS, Redux, RTK Query&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Backend - Django, DRF, Postgres&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;DevOps - Docker, Github Actions, Terraform, AWS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
