&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work directly with our CEO, CTO, and a handful of other engineers to build full stack features and improvements to the product&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Work across the entire stack using cutting edge frameworks, tools, and own execution&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Take true end-to-end ownership of your work and lead key components of our product roadmap&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Refine the SDLC &amp;amp; CI/CD pipelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintaining our AWS infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
